<lb ed="T" n="0820b11"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="001"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead>佛說越難經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0820b12" ed="T"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0820b13"/><byline cb:type="Translator">西晉<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0820014" resp="Taisho">居士＝清信士【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820014" type="mod">居士【大】，清信士【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820014"><lem wit="【大】">居士</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">清信士</rdg></app>聶承遠譯</byline>
<lb ed="T" n="0820b14"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT14p0820b1401">聞如是：</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0820b1404">一時，佛在波羅奈私<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0820015" resp="Taisho">國賢者飛鳥聚＝園【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0820015" resp="CBETA">國賢者飛鳥聚【大】，園【宮】</note><app n="0820015"><lem wit="【大】">國，賢者飛鳥
<lb n="0820b15" ed="T"/>聚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">園</rdg></app>。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0820b1502" rend="inline"><note n="0820016" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">彼＝是【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820016" type="mod">彼【大】，是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820016"><lem wit="【大】">彼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">是</rdg></app>時，國中有四姓長者，名曰越難，大豪
<lb n="0820b16" ed="T"/><note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0820017" type="orig">富珍奇＝貴珍琦【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820017" type="mod">富珍奇【大】，貴珍琦【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820017"><lem wit="【大】">富，珍奇</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">貴珍琦</rdg></app>珠寶、牛馬、田宅甚眾多。難為人慳貪
<lb n="0820b17" ed="T"/>嫉妬，不信道德、不喜布施。日未沒，常勅門監，
<lb ed="T" n="0820b18"/>有來乞<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0820018" resp="Taisho">〔匃〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0820018" resp="CBETA">匃【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820018"><lem wit="【大】">匃</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>者，勿得通<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0820019" resp="Taisho">也＝之【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820019" type="mod">也【大】，之【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820019"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">之</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0820b19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT14p0820b1901">難有<note n="0820020" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔一〕－【宋】【宮】</note><note n="0820020" type="mod" resp="CBETA">一【大】，〔－〕【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0820020"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>子，名<note n="0820021" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔曰〕－【宮】</note><note n="0820021" type="mod" resp="CBETA">曰【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0820021"><lem wit="【大】">曰</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>栴檀，亦復慳貪。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0820b1913">難後壽盡，
<lb ed="T" n="0820b20"/><note n="0820022" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔還〕－【宮】</note><note n="0820022" type="mod" resp="CBETA">還【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0820022"><lem wit="【大】">還</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>生其國中，為盲乞婦作子。其夫言：「汝身
<lb n="0820b21" ed="T"/>有重病，今復懷軀，<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0820023" resp="Taisho">我＋（以）【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820023" type="mod">我【大】，我以【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820023"><lem wit="【大】">我</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">我以</rdg></app>貧窮無以衣食，汝便
<lb n="0820b22" ed="T"/>自去。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0820b2203">婦受教出門<note n="0820024" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔外〕－【宮】</note><note n="0820024" type="mod" resp="CBETA">外【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0820024"><lem wit="【大】">外</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，未遠得大聚糞，便止
<lb ed="T" n="0820b23"/>其中。至九月生一子，兩目<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0820025" type="orig">復＝悉【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0820025" resp="CBETA">復【大】，悉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820025"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">悉</rdg></app>盲，其母<note n="0820026" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔行〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820026" type="mod">行【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820026"><lem wit="【大】">行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>乞
<lb n="0820b24" ed="T"/>食養之。至年七歲，<note n="0820027" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔其〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820027" type="mod">其【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820027"><lem wit="【大】">其</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>母言：「我養汝大久，且
<lb n="0820b25" ed="T"/>自行<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0820028" resp="Taisho">拄＝持【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0820028" resp="CBETA">拄【大】，持【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820028"><lem wit="【大】">拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">持</rdg></app>杖，取食器行乞，當自悲言：『世間貧
<lb n="0820b26" ed="T"/>者最為苦惱。今我薄命生貧家，兩目復盲無
<lb ed="T" n="0820b27"/>所<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0820029" resp="Taisho">見＋（者）【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0820029" resp="CBETA">見【大】，見者【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820029"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">見者</rdg></app>，復為人所輕易。今<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0820030" place="foot text">有乞＝與【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820030" type="mod">有乞【大】，與【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820030"><lem wit="【大】">有乞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">與</rdg></app>我少所<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0820031" resp="Taisho">飲食＝飯【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0820031" resp="CBETA">飲食【大】，飯【宮】</note><app n="0820031"><lem wit="【大】">飲
<lb n="0820b28" ed="T"/>食</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">飯</rdg></app>，愈我飢者，譬如天雨，渴者得飲。』」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0820b2814" rend="inline">兒聞母
<lb n="0820b29" ed="T"/>說如是，便行家家乞匃，復到栴檀家。其子
<pb ed="T" n="0820c" xml:id="T14.0537.0820c"/>
<lb n="0820c01" ed="T"/>適到時，守門者<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0820032" place="foot text">適＝暫【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0820032" resp="CBETA">適【大】，暫【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820032"><lem wit="【大】">適</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">暫</rdg></app>小出，盲兒<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0820033" resp="Taisho">徑入＝往入【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0820033" resp="CBETA">徑入【大】，往入【宮】</note><app n="0820033"><lem wit="【大】">徑入</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">往入</rdg></app><note n="0820034" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">前到＝至【三】，前至【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0820034" resp="CBETA">前到【大】，至【宋】【元】【明】，前至【宮】</note><app n="0820034"><lem wit="【大】">前到</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">至</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">前至</rdg></app>中
<lb n="0820c02" ed="T"/>庭，如母教說之。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0820c0207" rend="inline">時，栴檀在高<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0820035" type="orig">觀＝樓【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820035" type="mod">觀【大】，樓【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820035"><lem wit="【大】">觀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">樓</rdg></app>上聞其<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0820036" type="orig">語＝言【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820036" type="mod">語【大】，言【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820036"><lem wit="【大】">語</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">言</rdg></app>，
<lb ed="T" n="0820c03"/>大<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0820037" place="foot text">怒＋（便）【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0820037" resp="CBETA">怒【大】，怒便【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820037"><lem wit="【大】">怒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">怒便</rdg></app>呼守門者問之：「誰內此盲<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0820038" place="foot text">〔乞〕－【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0820038">乞【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0820038"><lem wit="【大】">乞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>兒者？」<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0820039" type="orig">門監大恐怖＝監門人大懅【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820039" type="mod">門監大恐怖【大】，監門人大懅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820039"><lem wit="【大】">門
<lb n="0820c04" ed="T"/>監大恐怖</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">監門人大懅</rdg></app>，即<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0820040" resp="Taisho">牽＝掣【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820040" type="mod">牽【大】，掣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820040"><lem wit="【大】">牽</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">掣</rdg></app>盲兒<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0820041" type="orig">撲＝撥【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820041" type="mod">撲【大】，撥【宮】</note><app n="0820041"><lem wit="【大】">撲</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">撥</rdg></app>於門外，傷其頭面，
<lb n="0820c05" ed="T"/>復<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0820042" type="orig">折＋（其）【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820042" type="mod">折【大】，折其【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820042"><lem wit="【大】">折</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">折其</rdg></app>右臂，壞其食器，飯散<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0820043" place="foot text">其＝於【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0820043" resp="CBETA">其【大】，於【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820043"><lem wit="【大】">其</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">於</rdg></app>地，身體大痛。
<lb n="0820c06" ed="T"/><note n="0820044" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">兒＋（呌）【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0820044" resp="CBETA">兒【大】，兒呌【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820044"><lem wit="【大】">兒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">兒呌</rdg></app>呼悲啼，其母聞之，即走到兒所，<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0820045" resp="Taisho">〔言〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820045" type="mod">言【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820045"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>：「何等
<lb ed="T" n="0820c07"/>弊人嬈我子者？我子尚小，<note n="0820046" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">兩＝其【宮】</note><note n="0820046" type="mod" resp="CBETA">兩【大】，其【宮】</note><app n="0820046"><lem wit="【大】">兩</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">其</rdg></app>目復盲，有何
<lb ed="T" n="0820c08"/><note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0820047" type="orig">〔等〕－【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820047" type="mod">等【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0820047"><lem wit="【大】">等</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>過，<note n="0820048" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">乃取如是＝而取之爾【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820048" type="mod">乃取如是【大】，而取之爾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820048"><lem wit="【大】">乃取如是</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">而取之爾</rdg></app>。何壹感天？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0820c0811">兒對母言：「我
<lb ed="T" n="0820c09"/><note n="0820049" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">到＝至【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820049" type="mod">到【大】，至【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820049"><lem wit="【大】">到</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">至</rdg></app>此門中乞，有高聲人，呼多力人<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0820050" type="orig">牽撲傷我身＝掣撲折傷我【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820050" type="mod">牽撲傷我身【大】，掣撲折傷我【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820050"><lem wit="【大】">牽撲傷
<lb n="0820c10" ed="T"/>我，身</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">掣撲折傷我</rdg></app>體大痛如是，今且死不久。」時門上有
<lb n="0820c11" ed="T"/>守神，<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0820051" resp="Taisho">〔便〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820051" type="mod">便【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820051"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>謂之言：「汝得是痛，尚為小耳，其
<lb n="0820c12" ed="T"/>大在後。汝坐前世有財不布<note n="0820052" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">施＋（今）【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0820052" resp="CBETA">施【大】，施今【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820052"><lem wit="【大】">施</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">施今</rdg></app>，故得勤苦。
<lb n="0820c13" ed="T"/>世間富貴無有常，富貴而不布施，如無有財
<lb ed="T" n="0820c14"/>等<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0820053" place="foot text">也＝耳【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0820053" resp="CBETA">也【大】，耳【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820053"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">耳</rdg></app>。死更苦痛，<note n="0820054" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">乃＝迺【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820054" type="mod">乃【大】，迺【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820054"><lem wit="【大】">乃</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">迺</rdg></app>愁悔，當復何益？」<note n="0820055" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">時＝如是【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820055" type="mod">時【大】，如是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820055"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">如是</rdg></app>觀
<lb n="0820c15" ed="T"/>者甚眾多，各各自語，其聲遠聞。</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0820c16"/><p xml:id="pT14p0820c1601">佛時從念道覺，與諸比丘俱入城<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0820056" place="foot text">〔分衛〕－【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0820056">分衛【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0820056"><lem wit="【大】">分衛</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0820057" place="foot text">佛＝遙見之便【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820057" type="mod">佛【大】，遙見之便【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820057"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">遙見之便</rdg></app>
<lb n="0820c17" ed="T"/>問阿難：「是何等聲？<note n="0820058" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">怱怱乃＝迺【宮】</note><note n="0820058" type="mod" resp="CBETA">怱怱乃【大】，迺【宮】</note><app n="0820058"><lem wit="【大】">怱怱乃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">迺</rdg></app>如是。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0820c1713" rend="inline">阿難<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0820059" type="orig">〔便〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0820059" resp="CBETA">便【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820059"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="T" n="0820c18"/>白佛，說<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0820060" place="foot text">盲＋（兒）【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820060" type="mod">盲【大】，盲兒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820060"><lem wit="【大】">盲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">盲兒</rdg></app>子母本<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0820061" place="foot text">事＝末【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0820061" type="mod">事【大】，末【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820061"><lem wit="【大】">事</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">末</rdg></app>已，便叉手白佛：「願哀
<lb n="0820c19" ed="T"/><note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0820062" type="orig">矜＝憐【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0820062" resp="CBETA">矜【大】，憐【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820062"><lem wit="【大】">矜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">憐</rdg></app>，到此兒所。」佛默然不應。分衛還飯已，便
<lb n="0820c20" ed="T"/>往視之。見盲兒<note n="0820063" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">創＝瘡【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0820063" resp="CBETA">創【大】，瘡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820063"><lem wit="【大】">創</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">瘡</rdg></app>痛，以手摩其頭，目便即
<pb ed="T" n="0821a" xml:id="T14.0537.0821a"/>
<lb n="0821a01" ed="T"/>開，<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0821001" type="orig">〔折〕－【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0821001" type="mod">折【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0821001"><lem wit="【大】">折</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>傷處即愈，因自識宿命。佛問：「汝是前
<lb ed="T" n="0821a02"/>世長者字<note n="0821002" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">（越）＋難【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0821002" resp="CBETA">難【大】，越難【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0821002"><lem wit="【大】">難</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">越難</rdg></app>不？」對言：「是也。」</p>
<lb n="0821a03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT14p0821a0301">佛告阿難：「人居世間甚<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0821003" resp="Taisho">〔懃苦〕－【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0821003" resp="CBETA">懃苦【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0821003"><lem wit="【大】">懃苦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>愚癡，一世父
<lb ed="T" n="0821a04"/>子不相識知。」</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0821a05"/><p xml:id="pT14p0821a0501"><note n="0821004" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">（爾時…意）九字＝佛故說偈言【三】，佛便說偈言【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0821004" type="mod">（爾時…意）九字【大】，佛故說偈言【宋】【元】【明】，佛便說偈言【宮】</note><app cb:word-count="9" n="0821004"><lem wit="【大】">爾時佛說經，解散其意</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">佛故說偈言</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">佛便說偈言</rdg></app>：</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0821a06"/><lg rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em" xml:id="lgT14p0821a0601">「<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0821005" type="orig">（人求…果）四句二十字∞（有身…常）六句三十字【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0821005" type="mod">（人求…果）四句二十字【大】∞（有身…常）六句三十字【宮】</note><app n="0821005"><lem wit="【大】"><l>人求子索財，</l><l>於此二事中，</l>
<lb n="0821a07" ed="T"/><l>甚憂勤苦痛，</l><l>他人而得果。</l></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">有身不能保何況子與財譬如夏月暑息止樹下涼須臾當復去世間無有常</rdg></app>
<lb n="0821a08" ed="T"/><note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0821006" type="orig">（人求…果）四句二十字∞（有身…常）六句三十字【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0821006" type="mod">（有身…常）六句三十字【大】∞（人求…果）四句二十字【宮】</note><app n="0821006"><lem wit="【大】"><l>有身不能保，</l><l>何況子與財？</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0821a09"/><l>譬如夏月<note n="0821007" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">暑＝熱【宮】</note><note n="0821007" type="mod" resp="CBETA">暑【大】，熱【宮】</note><app n="0821007"><lem wit="【大】">暑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">熱</rdg></app>，</l><l>息止樹下涼，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0821a10"/><l>須臾當復去，</l><l>世間無有常。」</l></lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">人求子索財於此二事中甚憂勤苦痛他人而得果</rdg></app></lg>
<lb ed="T" n="0821a11"/><p xml:id="pT14p0821a1101">阿難白佛：「此兒命盡，當趣何道？」佛言：「當入大
<lb ed="T" n="0821a12"/>泥梨中一宿。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0821a1206">佛說是<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0821008" type="orig">〔經〕－【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0821008" type="mod">經【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0821008"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>時，八萬餘人皆棄三
<lb n="0821a13" ed="T"/>垢得法眼。諸弟子皆歡喜，為佛作禮而去。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="T" n="0821a14"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>佛說越難經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
